    "description": "Delivery Impossible is a crazy delivery simulator that will suit both adult players and young racing fans. <strong>Add this game to your wishlist!</strong><br><br>Dodge <strong>UFOs</strong>, fight <strong>military caterpillars</strong>, destroy everything you see. Above all, get your cargo to the destination point. At any cost!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >10 Unique Vehicles</h2>Unlock all <strong>10 unique vehicles</strong> available in the game. Each of 10 main levels can be completed with <strong>any</strong> vehicle - even if it doesn't seem appropriate at first glance. All vehicles have unique design and characteristics - you will have to familiarize yourself with them thoroughly to succeed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335550/extras/67c9da0dfe2132ab61435c66201c6991.poster.avif?t=1716237817\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335550/extras/67c9da0dfe2132ab61435c66201c6991.webm?t=1716237817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335550/extras/67c9da0dfe2132ab61435c66201c6991.mp4?t=1716237817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destroyable Environment</h2>Almost all game objects, except for buildings and some obstacles, <strong>can be destroyed</strong>! We took special care of how the physics work in Delivery Impossible, so that you get the most out of smashing the environment!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335550/extras/534fe13599602e7de076603639548538.poster.avif?t=1716237817\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335550/extras/534fe13599602e7de076603639548538.webm?t=1716237817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335550/extras/534fe13599602e7de076603639548538.mp4?t=1716237817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unbelievable Cargo Loads</h2>To complete the game, you'll need to perform <strong>more than 100 different deliveries</strong>. Buy cars to unlock new levels and revisit completed tracks with new vehicles. We tried to make <strong>every</strong> delivery memorable!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335550/extras/33f15707afed3d693de212e0388e24cc.poster.avif?t=1716237817\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335550/extras/33f15707afed3d693de212e0388e24cc.webm?t=1716237817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335550/extras/33f15707afed3d693de212e0388e24cc.mp4?t=1716237817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Levels and Routes</h2>Explore 10 highly detailed routes. The game features a variety of weather conditions and times of day, from sizzling desert heat to deep forest night.<br><br><strong>Here's what we've got for you:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A mad tour through cozy city streets<br></li><li>Watermelon delivery in the countryside<br></li><li>Dinosaur skeleton transportation down a deserted railroad.<br></li><li>Jumping and flying on the skyscraper roofs<br></li><li>Escape from a UFO deep in the forest at night<br></li><li>Candy delivery in the &quot;Sweet Kingdom&quot;.<br></li><li>Dangerous rappelling down a quarry with a truckload of dynamite<br></li><li>A crazy test drive of a giant monster truck.</li></ul>...and even more!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335550/extras/dbd68d243f77c280a271d00d393f95f1.avif?t=1716237817\" width=400 height=172 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Future</h2>At the end of the game you are in for a little surprise. The last and the craziest level will be revealed only after passing 9 main routes!<br><br>In the upcoming update we’ll add 5 more extra missions: <strong>Mommy's errands</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Achievements</h2>There are more than 30 unique achievements in the game. To unlock them all, you'll have to try really hard!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335550/extras/488daf68fdf47c332b423ca63109e9d0.avif?t=1716237817\" width=400 height=78 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Still Hesitating?</h2>Try the Delivery Impossible demo! We guarantee - it won't leave you cold!",
